description	"B1-Series Demolitions Battle Droid

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (3)
- E-60R Rocket Launcher
-- 6 Thermal Rockets

The demolitions battle droid was a B1 battle droid used by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars.
They often carried rocket launchers, mines, thermal detonators, and a blaster pistol.
They were distinguished by their blue markings, and were not to be confused with the OOM pilot battle droid, which also had blue markings."